    "title": "Immediate Requirement Logistics Manager at IRCTC Logistics Ventures Solutions",
    "description": "IRCTC Logistics Ventures Solutions, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Logistics Manager for our Surat operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout IRCTC Logistics Ventures Solutions:\nIRCTC Logistics Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n• Coordinate with warehousing teams for inbound and outbound operations\n• Manage reverse logistics and return merchandise authorization\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Implement warehouse management systems (WMS) and track KPIs\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n• Implement cost-saving initiatives in transportation and warehousing\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n• Proficiency in WMS\n• Proficiency in TMS\n• Proficiency in Route Optimization\n• Proficiency in Fleet Management\n• Proficiency in GPS Tracking Systems\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Referral bonus program\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Surat, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with IRCTC Logistics Ventures Solutions!",
